reviewText: Great Copy! My husband and I decided to purchase this item as our son is a fanatic of the audubon series and anything animal related. He already owns a few others so adding this one to his collection as a b-day present was a delight. it was on his bday wish list but to have actually received it made him overjoyed
I liked this movie okay.  I wished it could have been a bit more thorough and detailed, but it was fine as-is.
